[%cal Gf7f5] with the important point being} 13. g4 Nd4 $1 {with nice play for
Black.}) 12... Nxe7 {[%cal Gh5f4] Black is doing great.}) 11... Bxf6 12. Nd5 {
[%csl Gd5]} b5 {[%csl Gc4]} 13. axb5 axb5 14. Bb3 g6 $11 {[%cal Gf6g7,Gg8h8,
