({or} 10. Bc4 dxc3 11. Nxc3 Nf6 12. Nd5 d6 {[%csl Ge5] White has to prove
sufficient compensation.}) 10... dxc3 11. Nxc3 {I also checked another
recapture} (11. Bxc3 {[%csl Ge5]} Qe7 12. Na3 {[%cal Ga3c4] Here we have a
