8... Nf6 $1 {[%csl Gh5]} 9. Qd2 {Herrera Reyes,J-Yeletsky,I Chess.com INT 2021
and Black should have played} Be6 $146 10. O-O Qd7 $15 {with great position.})
(7. Nd2 {scores extremely well for White, but in my opinion Black is doing
well after} Nge7 8. Nc4 (8. O-O {transposes to 7.0-0}) 8... Be6 {[%csl Gd5]} 9.
Ne3 (9. h4 {happened in two games. Black always responded with 9...h5, while I
believe} h6 $146 {is a better solution.} 10. Nd5 (10. h5 g5) 10... Nb4 $5 {
[%csl Gd5]} 11. Nxe7 Qxe7 12. h5 Qd7 13. Ne3 Nc6 14. c3 Ne7 $13 {[%csl Gd5]
with roughly equal play.}) 9... Qd7 10. Ncd5 O-O 11. O-O Bh3 {[%csl Gg2]} 12.
