ready to meet} (17. f4 {with} f5) 17... d5 18. Qxg6 hxg6 19. exd5 Bxd5 $11 {
with equal endgame.}) (10. Nxb6 axb6 11. c3 O-O 12. Qc2 {[%cal Gf1e3]} Be6 13.
